      <p>The content on this page is reviewed and maintained by the accounting team at <strong>TechBrot Inc.</strong>, a Delaware-incorporated independent Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor firm. Texas&ndash;specific statutory references, tax rates, and operational context reflect direct operational knowledge and are reviewed against current <a href="https://comptroller.texas.gov/" rel="noopener nofollow">Texas Comptroller of Public Accounts</a> guidance.</p>
      <p>Where Texas tax rates or regulatory thresholds are subject to revision (the franchise-tax no-tax-due threshold, margin-method caps, sales-tax rates), this page is updated as changes take effect.</p>
